reviewText: Watched this video a couple of times and it save major bucks and time. Very good at walking through step by step. Very valuable video for me.

Though this video was technically good it was really "dated" and that made me loose enthusiasm.  I wanted information on kitchens of today.  It was mostly my fault.  I should have looked at the publication date.  Otherwise there were basic tips that really don't change I guess.
Easy to understand, informative.  Told me what I needed to know to rebuild my bathroom.
